SNAPCAT
=======

Snapcat - Combine directory tree, file contents, and SHA256 hashes into a
single JSON or Markdown document. Perfect for snapshots, code reviews,
LLM context building, and auditing.

Version  : 0.2.2
License  : GPL-3.0
Website  : https://github.com/mroczect/snapcat   (placeholder)
Rust     : Edition 2024


